ages.reverse()` at the end - so they are returned in ASC order\n\nIn `im_bloc.da
rt` `_onLoadMessages`:\n- `var allMessages = [...result.items, ...currentMessage
s];`\n- For pagination (`cursor != null`), `currentMessages` are the already loa
ded messages, and `result.items` are the older messages fetched. Since result.it
ems are in ASC order (oldest to newest among the fetched batch), putting them be
fore currentMessages gives [older, newer_current]. This is correct.\n\n10. Wait 
