om the fullstack feature template were not executed or even mentioned:\n   - `ma
ke test` — explicitly NOT run (developer blames environment)\n   - `make test-bd
d` — not mentioned at all\n   - `make check-contract-sync` — not mentioned at al
l\n   - `make build` — not mentioned at all (only `flutter build apk` was run)\n
